<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> قِرَاءَةً.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَسُجُودَ سَهْوٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَتِلَاوَةً.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَسُتْرَةً.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَدُعَاءَ قُنُوتٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٦]</span> وَتَشَهُّدًا أَوَّلَ إِذَا سُبِقَ بِرَكْعَةٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَالأَوْلَى أَنْ يَشْرَعَ فِي أَفْعَالِهَا بَعْدَ إِمَامٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- فَإِنْ وَافَقَهُ فِيهَا،<span style="color:#006d98"> أَوْ سَلَامٍ:</span> كُرِهَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ سَبَقَهُ:</span> حَرُمَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ كَبَّرَ لِإِحْرَامٍ مَعَهُ أَوْ قَبْلَ إِتْمَامِهِ:</span> لَمْ تَنْعَقِدْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَإِنْ سَلَّمَ قَبْلَهُ عَمْدًا بِلَا عُذْرٍ أَوْ سَهْوًا،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَلَمْ يُعِدْهُ:</span> بَعْدَهُ بَطَلَتْ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَسُنَّ لإِمَامٍ:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- التَّخْفِيفُ مَعَ الإِتْمَامِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَتَطْوِيلُ قِرَاءَةِ الأُولَى عَنِ الثَّانِيَةِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- وَانْتِظَارُ دَاخِلٍ إِنْ لَمْ يَشُقَّ عَلَى مَأْمُومٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>